text: Valeria Cătescu (born 17 September 1953) is a Romanian rower. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Romania Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Galați County
